Box-Model : It is used for designing and layout

The CSS box model is essentially a box that wraps around every HTML element.    
It consists of margin, borders, padding and actual content

Every content is placed/displayed on UI is wrapped under the rectangular shape box

Box Model : All the content which is rendering on the UI is rendered under the rectangular box 

Four imp parts of Box-Model : 
content
padding
border
margin

Padding : It is nothing but the space between content and border
Margin : It is gap that comes after border, like inside gap from border(to content) is padding whereas outside gap from border is margin
